title: Tom Waits & Peter Murphy - Christmas Sucks
description:
This is not actually Tom Waits and Peter Murphy singing, but some people with very similar voices.
Quote:
Porn Orchard&#039;s tune was included because it&#039;s often circulated as "Peter Murphy and Tom Waits" (strange bedfellows indeed!) but was in fact by Porn Orchard and the Opal Foxx Quartet for a 1993 compilation by the Athens, GA magazine, Flagpole&#039;s "The Mother of All Flagpole Christmas Albums". The impressions are top notch. Curtiss Pernice played the part of Tom Waits and Ted Hafer did Peter Murphy (of Bauhaus).

Enjoy...
